10 chapter[has graduated from a Commission on Dental Accreditation (CODA)
11 accredited dental school and has been conferred with the degree of "Doctor of
12 Medical Dentistry" (D.M.D.) or "Doctor of Dental Surgery" (D.D.S.)];
