24 2. Diagnoses or treats diseases or lesions of human teeth or jaws, or
25 attempts to correct malpositions thereof;[, or who ]
26 3. Diagnoses or treats disorders, or deficiencies of the oral cavity and
27 adjacent associated structures;[, or who ]
