20 Section 4. KRS 313.030 is amended to read as follows:
21 (1) The license or registration held by a dentist, dental hygienist, or dental assistant
22 shall be valid for a period of two (2) years.
23 (2) Each license or registration held by a dentist, dental hygienist, or dental assistant
24 shall expire on December 31. A dentist's license shall expire in odd-numbered
25 years, while all other licenses or registrations issued by the board shall expire in
26 even-numbered years.
27 (3) Each license or registration held by any person issued under the provisions of this
