15 requirements of administrative regulations promulgated by the board.
16 (5) An application for renewal of a license or registration shall be completed online or,
17 if a written request is made to the board prior to November 1 of the year of
18 expiration, a paper application shall be sent to the last known address of each
19 licensee or certified or registered person requesting a paper application.
20 (6) Any person engaging in any practice or activity regulated by the board during the
21 time his or her license or registration has lapsed shall be considered practicing with
22 an expired license or registration and shall be subject to the penalties provided for
23 violations of this chapter.
