21 technique, basic placement technique, nitrous oxide administration,
22 recordkeeping, armamentarium exercise, local anesthesia and nitrous oxide,
23 techniques of maxillary anesthesia, techniques of mandibular injections,
24 partner injections and partner administration of nitrous oxide,
25 neurophysiology, pharmacology of local anesthetics and nitrous oxide,
26 pharmacology of vasoconstrictors, physical and psychological evaluation,
27 local and systemic complications, and contraindications;
