20 Section 13. KRS 313.090 is amended to read as follows:
21 (1) In accordance with the provisions of KRS Chapter 13B, all discipline for which the
22 board is authorized to conduct investigations, hold hearings, and impose
23 punishments is delegated to the executive director, board attorney, and hearing
24 panel as provided in this section.
25 (2) Any person may make a complaint to the executive director that a dentist, dental
26 hygienist, dental assistant, or other person licensed or registered by the board has
27 violated a provision of this chapter, an administrative regulation promulgated by the
Page 26 of 33
BR211000.100 - 2110 - XXXX 3/11/2026 2:43 PM Jacketed

